{
  "openapi": "3.1.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "FunASR-API Server",
    "description": "基于FunASR的语音识别API服务",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "paths": {
    "/stream/v1/asr": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "ASR"
        ],
        "summary": "语音识别（支持长音频）",
        "description": "将音频文件转写为文本，兼容阿里云语音识别 RESTful API。\n\n## 功能特性\n- 支持多种音频格式：WAV, MP3, M4A, FLAC, OGG, AAC, AMR 等\n- 自动音频格式检测和转换\n- 支持长音频自动分段识别（返回带时间戳的分段结果）\n- 最大文件大小：{settings.MAX_AUDIO_SIZE // (1024 * 1024)}MB（可通过环境变量 MAX_AUDIO_SIZE 配置）\n\n## 可用模型\n- **paraformer-large**（默认）：高精度中文语音识别，内置VAD+标点（离线/实时）\n\n## 音频输入方式\n1. **请求体上传**：将音频二进制数据作为请求体发送\n2. **URL 下载**：通过 `audio_address` 参数指定音频文件 URL\n\n## 注意事项\n- `vocabulary_id` 参数用于传递热词，格式：`热词1 权重1 热词2 权重2`（如：`阿里巴巴 20 腾讯 15`）\n- 音频会自动转换为 16kHz 采样率进行识别",
        "operationId": "asr_transcribe_stream_v1_asr_post",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "识别成功",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "anyOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ASRSuccessResponse"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ASRErrorResponse"
                    }
                  ],
                  "title": "Response Asr Transcribe Stream V1 Asr Post",
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ASRSuccessResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "请求参数错误",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ASRErrorResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "认证失败",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ASRErrorResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "服务器内部错误",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ASRErrorResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "model_id",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "maxLength": 64,
              "default": "paraformer-large",
              "enum": [
                "paraformer-large"
              ],
              "example": "paraformer-large"
            },
            "description": "ASR 模型 ID。可选值：paraformer-large（高精度中文语音识别，内置VAD+标点（离线/实时））。默认：paraformer-large"
          },
          {
            "name": "audio_address",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "maxLength": 512,
              "example": ""
            },
            "description": "音频文件 URL（HTTP/HTTPS）。指定此参数时，将从 URL 下载音频而非读取请求体"
          },
          {
            "name": "sample_rate",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "enum": [8000, 16000, 22050, 24000],
              "default": 16000,
              "example": 16000
            },
            "description": "音频采样率（Hz），实际识别时会自动转换为 16kHz。支持：8000, 16000, 22050, 24000"
          },
          {
            "name": "enable_speaker_diarization",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "default": true,
              "example": true
            },
            "description": "是否启用说话人分离。启用后响应会包含 speaker_id 字段"
          },
          {
            "name": "word_timestamps",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "default": true,
              "example": true
            },
            "description": "是否返回字词级时间戳（仅 Qwen3-ASR 模型支持）"
          },
          {
            "name": "vocabulary_id",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "maxLength": 512,
              "example": "阿里巴巴 20 腾讯 15"
            },
            "description": "热词字符串，格式：`热词1 权重1 热词2 权重2`。权重范围 1-100，建议 10-30。可提升特定词汇的识别准确率"
          },
          {
            "name": "X-NLS-Token",
            "in": "header",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "minLength": 1,
              "maxLength": 256,
              "example": ""
            },
            "description": "访问令牌，用于身份认证。未配置 API_KEY 环境变量时可忽略"
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "description": "音频文件二进制数据。支持格式：WAV, MP3, M4A, FLAC, OGG, AAC, AMR 等。不使用 audio_address 参数时必需",
          "content": {
            "application/octet-stream": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "string",
                "format": "binary"
              }
            }
          },
          "required": false
        }
      }
    },
    "/stream/v1/asr/health": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "ASR"
        ],
        "summary": "ASR 服务健康检查",
        "description": "检查语音识别服务的运行状态和资源使用情况。\n\n## 返回信息\n- **status**: 服务状态（healthy/unhealthy/error）\n- **model_loaded**: 默认模型是否已加载\n- **device**: 当前推理设备（cuda:0/cpu）\n- **loaded_models**: 已加载的模型列表\n- **memory_usage**: GPU 显存使用情况（仅 GPU 模式）\n- **asr_model_mode**: 当前模型加载模式（offline/realtime/all）",
        "operationId": "health_check_stream_v1_asr_health_get",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ASRHealthCheckResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/stream/v1/asr/models": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "ASR"
        ],
        "summary": "获取可用模型列表",
        "description": "返回系统中所有可用的 ASR 模型信息。\n\n## 可用模型\n\n| 模型 ID | 名称 | 说明 | 支持实时 |\n|---------|------|------|----------|\n| qwen3-asr-1.7b | Qwen3-ASR 1.7B | 高性能多语言语音识别，vLLM后端，52种语言+方言 | ❌ |\n| qwen3-asr-0.6b | Qwen3-ASR 0.6B | 轻量版多语言ASR，适合小显存环境 | ❌ |\n| paraformer-large | Paraformer Large | 高精度中文语音识别 | ✅ |\n\n## 返回信息\n- **models**: 模型详细信息列表\n- **total**: 可用模型总数\n- **loaded_count**: 已加载到内存的模型数量\n- **asr_model_mode**: 当前模型加载模式",
        "operationId": "list_models_stream_v1_asr_models_get",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ASRModelsResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/ws/v1/asr/test": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "WebSocket ASR"
        ],
        "summary": "Websocket Asr Test Page",
        "description": "WebSocket ASR 测试页面",
        "operationId": "websocket_asr_test_page_ws_v1_asr_test_get",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "text/html": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "string"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/v1/models": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "OpenAI Compatible"
        ],
        "summary": "列出可用模型",
        "description": "返回当前可用的 ASR 模型列表（OpenAI `/v1/models` 兼容）。\n\n**可用模型：**\n\n| 模型 ID | 说明 |\n|---------|------|\n| `paraformer-large` | 高精度中文 ASR，内置 VAD+标点（默认） |\n\n**兼容性说明：**\n- `whisper-1` 等 OpenAI 模型 ID 会自动映射到默认模型\n- 支持 OpenAI SDK 和第三方客户端调用\n- 当前默认模型根据显存自动选择：\u003C32GB 用 0.6b，\u003E=32GB 用 1.7b",
        "operationId": "list_models_v1_models_get",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ModelsResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/v1/audio/transcriptions": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "OpenAI Compatible"
        ],
        "summary": "音频转写",
        "description": "将音频文件转写为文本（完全兼容 OpenAI Audio API）。\n\n**支持的音频格式：**\n`mp3`, `mp4`, `mpeg`, `mpga`, `m4a`, `wav`, `webm`, `flac`, `ogg`, `amr`, `pcm`\n\n**音频输入方式（二选一）：**\n1. **文件上传**：通过 `file` 参数上传音频文件（标准 OpenAI 方式）\n2. **URL 下载**：通过 `audio_address` 参数提供音频文件 URL（HTTP/HTTPS）\n\n**文件大小限制：**\n- 最大支持 2048MB（可通过 `MAX_AUDIO_SIZE` 环境变量配置）\n- OpenAI 原生限制为 25MB\n\n**说话人分离：**\n- 默认开启 (`enable_speaker_diarization=true`)\n- 启用后 `verbose_json` 格式的 segments 会包含 `speaker` 字段（如 \"说话人1\"）\n- 可设置 `enable_speaker_diarization=false` 关闭\n\n**输出格式：**\n| 格式 | Content-Type | 说明 |\n|------|-------------|------|\n| `json` | application/json | 简单 JSON，仅含 text 字段（默认） |\n| `text` | text/plain | 纯文本 |\n| `verbose_json` | application/json | 详细 JSON，含时间戳、分段和说话人 |\n| `srt` | text/plain | SRT 字幕格式 |\n| `vtt` | text/vtt | WebVTT 字幕格式 |\n\n**模型映射：**\n- `whisper-1` → 使用默认模型 (paraformer-large)\n- `paraformer-large` → 高精度中文 ASR\n\n**暂不支持的参数：**\n`prompt`、`temperature`、`timestamp_granularities` 参数已保留但暂不生效",
        "operationId": "create_transcription_v1_audio_transcriptions_post",
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "multipart/form-data": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Body_create_transcription_v1_audio_transcriptions_post"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "转写成功",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {

                },
                "example": {
                  "text": "今天天气不错，明天可能会下雨。"
                }
              },
              "text/plain": {
                "example": "今天天气不错，明天可能会下雨。"
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "请求错误",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": {
                  "error_code": "INVALID_PARAMETER",
                  "message": "File too large. Maximum size is 2048MB",
                  "task_id": "",
                  "timestamp": "2025-01-31T12:00:00Z",
                  "details": {

                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "认证失败",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": {
                  "error_code": "AUTHENTICATION_FAILED",
                  "message": "Invalid API key",
                  "task_id": "",
                  "timestamp": "2025-01-31T12:00:00Z",
                  "details": {

                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "Validation Error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "根路径",
        "description": "API服务根路径",
        "operationId": "root__get",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {

                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "schemas": {
      "ASRErrorResponse": {
        "properties": {
          "task_id": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Task Id",
            "description": "任务ID"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "integer",
            "title": "Status",
            "description": "状态码"
          },
          "message": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Message",
            "description": "响应消息"
          },
          "result": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Result",
            "description": "识别结果（错误时为空）",
            "default": ""
          }
        },
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "task_id",
          "status",
          "message"
        ],
        "title": "ASRErrorResponse",
        "description": "ASR错误响应模型",
        "example": {
          "message": "Gateway:ACCESS_DENIED:The token 'invalid_token' is invalid!",
          "result": "",
          "status": 40000001,
          "task_id": "8bae3613dfc54ebfa811a17d8a7a1234"
        }
      },
      "ASRHealthCheckResponse": {
        "properties": {
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Status",
            "description": "服务状态",
            "examples": [
              "healthy"
            ]
          },
          "version": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Version",
            "description": "服务版本",
            "examples": [
              "1.0.0"
            ]
          },
          "message": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Message",
            "description": "状态消息",
            "examples": [
              "Service is running normally"
            ]
          },
          "model_loaded": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "title": "Model Loaded",
            "description": "模型是否已加载"
          },
          "device": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Device",
            "description": "推理设备"
          },
          "loaded_models": {
            "anyOf": [
              {
                "items": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "type": "array"
              },
              {
                "type": "null"
              }
            ],
            "title": "Loaded Models",
            "description": "已加载的模型列表",
            "default": []
          },
          "memory_usage": {
            "anyOf": [
              {
                "additionalProperties": true,
                "type": "object"
              },
              {
                "type": "null"
              }
            ],
            "title": "Memory Usage",
            "description": "内存使用情况"
          },
          "asr_model_mode": {
            "anyOf": [
              {
                "type": "string"
              },
              {
                "type": "null"
              }
            ],
            "title": "Asr Model Mode",
            "description": "当前ASR模型加载模式"
          }
        },
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "status",
          "version",
          "message",
          "model_loaded",
          "device"
        ],
        "title": "ASRHealthCheckResponse",
        "description": "ASR健康检查响应模型",
        "example": {
          "asr_model_mode": "realtime",
          "device": "cuda:0",
          "loaded_models": [
            "paraformer-large"
          ],
          "memory_usage": {
            "gpu_memory_total": "8.0GB",
            "gpu_memory_used": "2.1GB"
          },
          "message": "ASR service is running normally",
          "model_loaded": true,
          "status": "healthy",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      },
      "ASRModelInfo": {
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Id",
            "description": "模型id"
          },
          "name": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Name",
            "description": "模型名称"
          },
          "engine": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Engine",
            "description": "引擎类型"
          },
          "description": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Description",
            "description": "模型描述"
          },
          "languages": {
            "items": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "type": "array",
            "title": "Languages",
            "description": "支持的语言列表"
          },
          "default": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "title": "Default",
            "description": "是否为默认模型",
            "default": false
          },
          "loaded": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "title": "Loaded",
            "description": "是否已加载",
            "default": false
          },
          "supports_realtime": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "title": "Supports Realtime",
            "description": "是否支持实时识别",
            "default": false
          },
          "offline_model": {
            "anyOf": [
              {
                "additionalProperties": true,
                "type": "object"
              },
              {
                "type": "null"
              }
            ],
            "title": "Offline Model",
            "description": "离线模型信息"
          },
          "realtime_model": {
            "anyOf": [
              {
                "additionalProperties": true,
                "type": "object"
              },
              {
                "type": "null"
              }
            ],
            "title": "Realtime Model",
            "description": "实时模型信息"
          },
          "asr_model_mode": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Asr Model Mode",
            "description": "当前ASR模型加载模式"
          }
        },
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "id",
          "name",
          "engine",
          "description",
          "languages",
          "asr_model_mode"
        ],
        "title": "ASRModelInfo",
        "description": "新的ASR模型信息模型，支持离线和实时模型分离",
        "example": {
          "asr_model_mode": "realtime",
          "default": true,
          "description": "高精度中文语音识别模型",
          "engine": "funasr",
          "id": "paraformer-large",
          "languages": [
            "zh"
          ],
          "loaded": true,
          "name": "Paraformer Large",
          "offline_model": {
            "exists": true,
            "path": "iic/speech_paraformer-large_asr_nat-zh-cn-16k-common-vocab8404-pytorch"
          },
          "realtime_model": {
            "exists": true,
            "path": "iic/speech_paraformer-large_asr_nat-zh-cn-16k-common-vocab8404-online"
          },
          "supports_realtime": true
        }
      },
      "ASRModelsResponse": {
        "properties": {
          "models": {
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ASRModelInfo"
            },
            "type": "array",
            "title": "Models",
            "description": "模型列表"
          },
          "total": {
            "type": "integer",
            "title": "Total",
            "description": "模型总数"
          },
          "loaded_count": {
            "type": "integer",
            "title": "Loaded Count",
            "description": "已加载模型数量"
          },
          "asr_model_mode": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Asr Model Mode",
            "description": "当前ASR模型加载模式"
          }
        },
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "models",
          "total",
          "loaded_count",
          "asr_model_mode"
        ],
        "title": "ASRModelsResponse",
        "description": "ASR模型列表响应模型",
        "example": {
          "asr_model_mode": "realtime",
          "loaded_count": 1,
          "models": [
            {
              "asr_model_mode": "realtime",
              "default": true,
              "description": "高精度中文语音识别模型",
              "engine": "funasr",
              "id": "paraformer-large",
              "languages": [
                "zh"
              ],
              "loaded": true,
              "name": "Paraformer Large",
              "offline_model": {
                "exists": true,
                "path": "iic/speech_paraformer-large_asr_nat-zh-cn-16k-common-vocab8404-pytorch"
              },
              "realtime_model": {
                "exists": true,
                "path": "iic/speech_paraformer-large_asr_nat-zh-cn-16k-common-vocab8404-online"
              },
              "supports_realtime": true
            }
          ],
          "total": 3
        }
      },
      "ASRSegment": {
        "properties": {
          "text": {
            "type": "string",
            "title": "Text",
            "description": "该段识别文本"
          },
          "start_time": {
            "type": "number",
            "title": "Start Time",
            "description": "段落开始时间（秒）"
          },
          "end_time": {
            "type": "number",
            "title": "End Time",
            "description": "段落结束时间（秒）"
          },
          "speaker_id": {
            "anyOf": [
              {
                "type": "string"
              },
              {
                "type": "null"
              }
            ],
            "title": "Speaker Id",
            "description": "说话人ID（如 说话人1），仅启用说话人分离时返回"
          },
          "word_tokens": {
            "anyOf": [
              {
                "items": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/WordToken"
                },
